[[=]]
+++ INCIDENT REPORT -- 2014/10/15
+++++ RITUAL FAILURE
[[/=]]

While performing the appeasement ritual, Agent Rossellini had allegedly worn an engagement ring which Rsr. Sophia McCormack, her fiancée, reported having an estimated value of 4,000 USD. It is believed this lapse in protocol was due to the heightened attraction and feelings of attachment from the effects of R-447.

